<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-right">420 ms</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Singapore (APAC)</td>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-right">210 ms</td>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-right">240 ms</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">S\u00e3o Paulo (South America)</td>
